parent"><a href="/voting/voting-at-the-polls/">Voting at the Polls</a></li><!----></ul><ul class="side-nav-group menu-list"><li class="group-parent"><a href="/voting/candidates-for-office/">Candidates for Office</a></li><!----></ul><ul class="side-nav-group menu-list"><li class="group-parent"><a href="/voting/current-elected-officials/">Elected Officials</a></li><!----></ul><ul class="side-nav-group menu-list"><li><a href="/voting/important-dates-for-voters/">Important Dates for Voters</a></li><!----></ul></div></div><div><div class="side-nav-parent"><!----></div></div><div><div class="side-nav-parent"><!----></div></div><div><div class="side-nav-parent"><!----></div></div><div><div class="side-nav-parent"><!----></div></div></aside></div><a href="#main" tabindex="1" class="skip-link" data-v-296f4200>Skip to main content</a><main id="main" tabindex="-1" class="column pt-0 main-body-copy" data-v-296f4200><h3 class="page-title" data-v-296f4200>Vote by Mail</h3><!----><p data-v-296f4200><p>All registered Philadelphia voters are entitled to vote by mail. You have two options: Mail-In Ballots and Absentee Ballots. An Absentee Ballot is only for people who will be outside the city on Election Day, or who have an illness or physical disability that would prevent them from attending the polls. Voters requesting an Absentee Ballot must provide a valid reason for receiving the ballot. Mail-In Ballots are available to all voters – no excuse needed!</p>
<div class="dyk"><strong>Did you know?</strong><br />
Absentee Ballots can also be requested due to a religious holiday or obligation and by members of the armed forces.</div>
<p><a href="https://www.pavoterservices.pa.gov/OnlineAbsenteeApplication/#/OnlineAbsenteeBegin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apply Online Today</a>! (Requires a Driver’s License/PennDOT ID or scanned signature)</p>
<p>If you want a Mail-In Ballot, make sure to answer no to the questions in the online application.<br />
<!-- [toggle on/off when two-months before an election until 3 weeks after an election] --><br />
Already applied? <a href="https://www.pavoterservices.pa.gov/Pages/BallotTracking.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Check the status of your application here</a>!<br />
<!-- [toggle on/off from 1 week after ballots start going out until 5 days before the election]

Need a replacement? Ballot never arrived? Request a replacement today  <a href="https://ballotform.vote.phila.gov/archive/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ballotform</a>!--></p>
<p>Rather mail in your application or having trouble with the online application?</p>
<table style="width: 100%;" border="1" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><a href="https://vote.phila.gov/files/absentee-ballot/mail_in_application.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download Mail-In Application</a></td>
<td><a href="https://vote.phila.gov/files/absentee-ballot/Absentee_Ballot_Application.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download Absentee Application</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="https://vote.phila.gov/files/absentee-ballot/mail_in_instructions.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mail-In Instructions</a></td>
